{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it a criminal offence to desecrate the Union Flag.",
        "additional_details": "The Union Flag represents the people of the UK. To have it disrespected in public is an insult.\r\nThere have been some people in the UK who have publicly set fire to the Union Flag, showing contempt for the very country who allows them safe residence.\r\nWe want to give our police force the power to arrest these people.",
        "background": "We want Parliament to pass legislation to punish anyone desecrating or disrespecting the Union Flag, which is our national flag. \r\nToo often you see gangs burning our flag in public.\r\nWe would suggest a fine of at least \u00a31000 and imprisonment of at least thirty days.",
